{
  "stem": "20580.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, like I tell you, it was 1942, before the holidays.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was 28 or 30 or the 1st of September when the-- before the killing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went away from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just reminded before.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I says my mother, goodbye.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my wife was that time with a little baby.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I went-- bye.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my mother says, I hope you're going see-- you're going to see the terrible tragedy world which is today on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I hope it's going to be a different world which I don't see after.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we share each other and came to the-- ghetto-- out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They did-- the guy let-- don't let us out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "How he-- but he bring in the Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And suddenly, they let me out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I just have to finish the work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "As I tell you before, we went out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that's the last time I see her with my wife.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother went with me together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was five people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My brother went with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We worked together.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As I told you last time, my brother-- I, I was-- I had hope he's going to live-- he's living.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But when I see this guy which I could call him up from here, another guy which was together with me also from the-- run away from the-- is-- I thought-- we were 10 people, three women and seven men.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We run away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we chart off in the bandits-- in the forest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the front-- the free-- he was running in front of me, he took a package.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I said-- I said, don't take any package.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I had my package.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't take it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I run after him like this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He told me, run away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When you're running away, try to get this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I run away.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
